{"tid":1460189,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】教育局反對罷課 斥鼓吹中學生不負責任","createTime":"2019-08-13T01:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T02:10:09.000Z","uid":56881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16c3abf89f9ecd6f4a5fb810509e107e58ac743d","tid":1460189,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-%E6%96%A5%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB-141200336.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%2590%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB-141200336.html&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y9%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=f2416bcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2-%E6%96%A5%E9%BC%93%E5%90%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB-141200336.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rm6cerFe6qksonrJa3zQ8Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190812a221512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Frm6cerFe6qksonrJa3zQ8Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190812a221512.jpg&h=791867cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學界呼籲每日到機場集會。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】香港大學、中文大學、科技大學等13所大學及大專院校學生會，今發表聯合聲明，呼籲市民即日起「無限期三罷」，同時有團體號召中學9月罷課。教育局發聲明反對中學及大專罷課，批評個別組織不顧修例工作停止的事實，鼓吹中學生罷課是不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n當局強調，任何人士不應利用學校作為表達政治訴求的場地，令未成年學生無辜被捲入政治漩渦，失去正常學習的機會，又呼籲家長與教師，幫助學生從多角度理解不同議題，培養客觀、持平的分析能力。至於大專罷課，教育局指師生罷課的行動，必定會影響院校的正常運作、日常教學及研究工作，擔心接連的紛擾，會對院校長遠發展造成負面影響。政府尊重專上院校享有院校自主，相信校方自行以適當方法處理，確保不參與罷課學生的學習不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n包括港大、中大、科大等8所資助大學、演藝學院、公開大學、恒生大學、樹仁大學及珠海學院發表聯合聲明，呼籲市民即日起「無限期三罷」，以反對警方「濫權濫暴」，形容警方「不受法律制裁才是使法治崩壞的元兇」；還呼籲市民由今天起，每日下午1時到機場參與集會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠你班官不負責任？"},{"pid":"d25d5b4a3e75f8d3b05be5f3ce39acf094b82867","tid":1460189,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:46:26.000Z","msg":"不顧修例工作停止的事實?<br />\n<br />\n點解柒婆死都唔撤回?<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"cce8a3eedc7b117804a777ddecf6fff06c6783ef","tid":1460189,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:49:04.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄我屌你老母"},{"pid":"778ff0cffc5bc55ec03d0fefc711b5e7a07ba21e","tid":1460189,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}